vista.db.dss
Class DSSDataWriter

java.lang.Object
  vista.db.dss.DSSDataWriter

public class DSSDataWriter
extends java.lang.Object

The class with native function calls to the HEC-DSS library. Only limited functionality of retrieving data is available at this time. Storing data options will be added later. Does not allow multithreaded access. However multi-user access is allowed.
